<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>187</hymn_number>
<author>Patea</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Damlai luipi dung leh vaiah vak mah leng,
 Malam khaw nuom Kanaan chu en zingin;
 Kipahna man lallukhuk chu a nai tai,
 Kapin khawvel hi mang sawt ta puong ka ie.

[V2]
 Sawt ta puona damsung lungkham buoina,
 Ei sapna Aw gi chu ka het leh;
 Lalchutphah vela a ngaklahnau aw chun,
 &quot;Hehpihte kahna a sawt taluoi a tiu.

[V3]
 2. Ka vakvaihna lui dung hi sau mahleh le,
 Ei puipa Mal Aksi en kawm zelin;
 Lawngchawlhna tang thiengtho chu ei tun ina,
 Ziechun hehpih len guol ngaih cheng kim tana.

[V4]
 3. Zuon zel ingka kumsawt huihchim nunna chu,
 Tuoilo-in van pakcha a lun zing ie;
 Belam No leh van pakcha lun zinghaw chu,
 Thisan vang in Aw, va tung ngei nang ka ie;

[V5]
 4. Gen minthang suong hawih tuol a ka len tiengleh,
 A sie ding leisiet nunglam ngai puong ie;
 Zie suong hawih Lalpa gam zemhawih a pang chu
 Tawp nei loin kumsawt in vak zing tana.</lyrics>
<title>Kanaan Chu En Zingin</title>
</song>